      "content": "oh wow, so u actually said u assumed they'd be more prone to violent outbursts because of their race? that's a pretty big leap to make just from a few sentences. do u think if the text said it was a crowd of \"older white professionals\" instead of \"young Black men and women\" u would have still used words like \"fury\" or \"riot\" or \"chaos\"?",
